{
  "stem": "14060.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, it was-- we lived very closely within the family and cousins and so on, as I have not enumerated, but I had two cousins of-- that was the middle brother, Julius, who was the one who became-- who survived.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was the only other Weiler who survived in our town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was a professor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "His sister, who did not survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then the lawyers had one son who was two years older me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He did also not survive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was in the same camp as me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And my brother and myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And this formed-- we were more or less the same age group, two years apart.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we used to play ping-pong and chess and football and, you know, the normal things which boys do, even these days.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, in addition-- so, therefore, how do you manage, foodwise on Shabbat?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At least in our house and in most better apartments or flats, they had these tiled ovens I'm sure you have seen, which-- you know, they were going from floor to ceiling practically, or just below ceiling, and were wide.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the front you put in wood or coal, mainly wood.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the more modern ones could burn through for 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, some didn't, so those had on the top built in-- if you go to Eastern Europe or even to Vienna or to Austria, you will see.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They call them kachelofen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were very beautiful, sort of colorful, with motives on the stoves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But some of them just had enough fuel in it to last overnight.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But by the morning, the fire went out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it had an opening like a chromium door, quite a deep door.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was customary and acceptable in Orthodox circles that you took milk in a pot.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
